9 AS INTRODUCED
10 An Act relating to cities and towns; amending 11 O.S.
2021, Section 17-105, as last amended by Section 1,
11 Chapter 287, O.S.L. 2024 (11 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
17-105), which relates to annual audits of
12 municipalities; requiring submission of annual
financial statement audit by certain municipalities;
13 permitting agreed-upon-procedures engagement;
requiring copies be filed with State Auditor and
14 Inspector six months after the close of the fiscal
year; amending 11 O.S. 2021, Section 17-107, as
15 amended by Section 3, Chapter 254, O.S.L. 2022 (11
O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 17-107), which relates to
16 failure of municipalities to file audit or agreed-
upon-procedures report; modifying period of
17 withholding funds; clarifying citation; clarifying
passage of House bill made section effectively not
18 repealed; directing the Oklahoma Tax Commission to
release certain funds; clarifying timeline for
19 release of funds by the Oklahoma Tax Commission;
providing for noncodification; providing an effective
20 date; and declaring an emergency.
21
22
23 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
